pgTitle: The X-Files Mythology, Volume 4 – Super Soldiers

rows.text: Three months after Mulder’s funeral, a former abductee awakens from the dead and Scully pins her hopes on resurrecting her partner; while Skinner is offered a loathsome deal by Krycek.
